fields.name: Coastal Grooves
fields.description: Coastal Grooves is Blood Orange's debut studio album. Released on August 30, 2011.

fields.name: Lonerism
fields.description: Lonerism is Tame Impala's second studio album, released on October 5, 2012, blending psychedelic rock with electronic influences.

fields.name: DAMN.
fields.description: DAMN. is Kendrick Lamar's fourth studio album, released on April 14, 2017. It's known for its complex storytelling and impactful lyrics.

fields.name: Kind of Blue
fields.description: Kind of Blue is a landmark album by Miles Davis, released on August 17, 1959. It's regarded as one of the greatest jazz albums of all time.

fields.name: In a Time Lapse
fields.description: In a Time Lapse is Ludovico Einaudi's album, released on January 21, 2013, blending classical and contemporary music.
